data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.LegacyIdentifiedCountCalc
data.value: A score of 1 or 0 depending on whether the peak overlaps with the retention time of an MS/MS identification.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.LegacyUnforcedCountScoreCalc
data.value: Fraction of transition peaks across all precursors for which "Coeluting" is true

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.LegacyUnforcedCountScoreDefaultCalc
data.value: Fraction of transition peaks for which "Coeluting" is true. Calculated using internal standard precursors if they exist, otherwise analyte precursors.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.LegacyUnforcedCountScoreStandardCalc
data.value: Fraction of transitions across internal standard precursors for which "Coeluting" is true.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.MQuestDefaultIntensityCalc
data.value: Log10 of the sum of the transition peak areas. Calculated using internal standard precursors if they exist, otherwise analyte precursors.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.MQuestDefaultIntensityCorrelationCalc
data.value: Normalized contrast angle of MS2 transition areas against library intensities, if that exist. Otherwise, dot product of MS1 transition areas against predicted isotope distribution. Calculated using internal standard precursors if they exist, otherwise analyte precursors.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.MQuestDefaultWeightedCoElutionCalc
data.value: MQuest co-elution score weighted by the sum of the transition areas. Calculated using internal standard precursors if they exist, otherwise analyte precursors.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.MQuestDefaultWeightedShapeCalc
data.value: MQuest shape score, weighted by the sum of the transition peak areas. Calculated using internal standard precursors if they exist, otherwise analyte precursors.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.MQuestIntensityCalc
data.value: Log10 of the sum of the transition peak areas across analyte precursors.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.MQuestIntensityCorrelationCalc
data.value: Normalized contrast angle of MS2 transition areas against library intensities. Calculated using analyte precursors.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.MQuestReferenceCorrelationCalc
data.value: Normalized contrast angle of the correlation between analyte and internal standard transition peak areas.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.MQuestRetentionTimePredictionCalc
data.value: Difference between predicted retention time and peak apex time.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.MQuestRetentionTimeSquaredPredictionCalc
data.value: Square of difference between predicted retention time and peak apex time.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.MQuestStandardIntensityCalc
data.value: Log10 of the sum of the transition peak areas across internal standard precursors.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.MQuestStandardIntensityCorrelationCalc
data.value: Normalized contrast angle of MS2 transition areas against library intensities. Calculated using internal standard precursors.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.MQuestStandardWeightedCoElutionCalc
data.value: MQuest co elution score, weighted by the sum of the transition peak areas. Calculated using internal standard precursors.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.MQuestStandardWeightedShapeCalc
data.value: MQuest shape score, weighted by the sum of the transition peak areas. Calculated using internal standard precursors.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.MQuestWeightedCoElutionCalc
data.value: MQuest co-elution score of analyte precursors weighted by the sum of the transition areas

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.MQuestWeightedReferenceCoElutionCalc
data.value: MQuest co elution score, weighted by the sum of the transition peak areas.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.MQuestWeightedReferenceShapeCalc
data.value: MQuest shape score, weighted by the sum of the transition peak areas.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.MQuestWeightedShapeCalc
data.value: MQuest shape score, weighted by the sum of the transition peak areas. Calculated using analyte precursors.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.NextGenCrossWeightedShapeCalc
data.value: The shape correlation score between MS1 ions and MS2 ions. Calculated using internal standard precursors if they exist, otherwise analyte precursors.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.NextGenIsotopeDotProductCalc
data.value: Normalized contrast angle of the MS1 transition areas against the predicted isotope distribution. Calculated using analyte precursor with the highest score.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.NextGenPrecursorMassErrorCalc
data.value: Average mass error across analyte MS1 transitions weighted by transition area.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.NextGenProductMassErrorCalc
data.value: Average mass error across analyte MS2 transitions weighted by transition area.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.NextGenSignalNoiseCalc
data.value: Log of the ratio of the peak height to the median intensity beyond the bounds of the peak. Calculated using analyte precursors.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.NextGenStandardProductMassErrorCalc
data.value: Average mass error across internal standard MS2 transitions weighted by transition area.

data.name: pwiz.Skyline.Model.Results.Scoring.NextGenStandardSignalNoiseCalc
data.value: Log of the ratio of the peak height to the median intensity beyond the bounds of the peak. Calculated using internal standard precursors.
